M\\u2009\\u2013\\u20099:00\\u202fPM", "Wednesday: 8:30\\u202fAM\\u2009\\u2013\\u20099:00\\u202fPM", "Thursday: 8:30\\u202fAM\\u2009\\u2013\\u20099:00\\u202fPM", "Friday: 8:30\\u202fAM\\u2009\\u2013\\u20092:30\\u202fPM", "Saturday: Closed", "Sunday: 9:00\\u202fAM\\u2009\\u2013\\u20099:00\\u202fPM"]}	[{"author_name": "shaina faerman", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117387333055985919276/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKT30gdeZ-m56DzPYiVOzoFHSBTJAZZG5JyKAftGDX6CChSfItjQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "a month ago", "text": "We were thrilled to find this dairy restaurant\\nWe had really good food and were treated really well\\nWe ordered the fries charcuterie plate\\nIt came with 3 types of fries : curly, regular, sweet potato, they were all so delicious and crispy and came with really good dips.\\nAnd we got 2 different types of pizza - both so good.\\nAnd pasta!!", "time": 1751340202, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Tracy Cooper", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115798409662034198088/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0-azwRlR5HKqwbDyeAPbyixrf8UtPiWrKMtn4ZYa2D5uiZ3rhBg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "rating": 4, "relative_time_description": "a month ago", "text": "It's a very decent place!\\nWe went to try their truffle pizza, and we left it. We also tried some sushi which was not as good. The rice was mushy, I think it was overcooked or left to sit too long.\\nThey do not have a liquor license but we're very prompt with refilling the waters. There is ample parking right outside and a cute area to walk around in with a fountain. My friend loved that it was European in the sense that they left you alone unless you asked them for something.\\nThere are two bathrooms that I saw, each was single person occupancy . Door was very squeaky and heavy and tricky to get locked but it was good  We had a nice time.", "time": 1751319256, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Cheryl Rivkin", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113272690408853040946/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEdFxgs_u9dMMT2Guzdt6LLefQKqQbGlcVHX9IelSRih_O6g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 3, "relative_time_description": "a week ago", "text": "Three weeks ago, we had a great meal with superb food.  I wanted to give 5 stars.  We asked for our pizzas well done and they were crisp and light.  Sea Bass was world class.  I note that more recently than this exceptional meal, however, we had a very disappointing experience.  We called ahead and booked a table for 9 people, plus babies in strollers.   We arrived at the restaurant just ahead of our scheduled time to find another party had just been seated in our table for 9.  They told us it would be a 10 minute wait, but eventually admitted that every table had just received menus and they had no idea when we could have a table.  We were actually 9 people plus two infants (all very carefully described before coming),   Pretty much all they could say was \\"Sorry.  Too bad.\\" We left.  Glad they have business, but lousy if you are trying to entertain or make plans.  The reservation meant nothing.  Why go through the fiction of pretending to take it?", "time": 1753932837, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Sara | TheBoxNY", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112017069387880991801/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISCZdYy7LNb03Bp7TfnDCH0s7XVgqrw9fBg9Oq2sSLkXEjCw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "a year ago", "text": "We landed in Boca for a quick business trip that ended up becoming unexpectedly longer. Tried out Carmela\\u2019