usercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvLm0E1AsNq3fb25G-9ux45GAtgwdJZF6uJHDEFyOM9Zls940=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 3, "relative_time_description": "12 months ago", "text": "I didn't realize at first that they even sold pizza but it was pretty good. The customer service did leave a lot to be desired as I saw in some other reviews. It really is amazing how much just smiling and being friendly can change a customer's entire experience. Please make a better customer service effort. Just start with smiling and saying hello.", "time": 1723758328, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Ab Gold", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116314054879005242849/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILX_aKCLgjTrA86nurCZwoRAJytvUkmGJolrqLr0V5o4Ft-mM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "2 months ago", "text": "Amazing place to get a really good fulfilling breakfast/lunch. You might think they're expensive.. 14 dollars for a tuna sandwich... It is NOT expensive for what you get. You get 2+ full BIG scoops of tuna in a sandwich plus a big variety of fresh veggies, and the same goes for the egg sandwiches (the egg sandwiches are only 10 bucks)\\n\\nReally GREAT service, even if I was not used to the style as a NY'er.\\n\\nOne thing they might fix though; when you make an omelette, PLEASE ask if the customer needs salt or pepper in it...\\n\\nOverall, highly recommended!\\n\\nYou're welcome \\ud83e\\udd17", "time": 1747416079, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Kseniia K", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101384788683770005132/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvn5CNLFSqP46AL-Dm0LmHXqxhmLF7GWGHTmB_OPDxI9c2_g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 1, "relative_time_description": "5 months ago", "text": "Update: I sent them email, as they asked in t