om/maps/contrib/108306483664919850405/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbSisPWSI48V7Ny2B-mL1KEL5015ZfCzNbHg1h87RUYoIeeJw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "5 months ago", "text": "I had a fantastic experience at Oasis Pizzeria & Bakery! The atmosphere is warm and inviting, and the staff is incredibly friendly and attentive. Their pizzas are perfectly crispy with fresh toppings, and the baked goods are absolutely delicious \\u2014 you can tell everything is made with care and quality ingredients. Whether you\\u2019re grabbing a quick bite or sitting down to enjoy a meal, this place is a hidden gem. Highly recommend trying their specialty pizzas and pastries. I\\u2019ll definitely be coming back!", "time": 1740279963, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "M.G One Home", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118374233214814452353/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1F_Av-8k91r2L1fL-PR2ez8btFrRLn3BYeh1Xk8TJjeLmdQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "6 months ago", "text": "What a place. The pizza is really good! We were 4 people and we ordered, Large Cheese Pizza, Spinach Kachapuri, The eggplant Sambusak and Greek Salad. Everything was delicious! You must try this Kosher pizza place!", "time": 1738779761, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "YAMIT ARAD", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111080574535934251095/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJulKrLv1FEompG5vlWeE026q3DdTuzkhPYNLo7eLIiivEYAWrsQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "2 months ago", "text": "\\u2b50\\ufe0f\\u2b50\\ufe0f\\u2b50\\ufe0f\\u2b50\\ufe0f\\u2b50\\ufe0f\\n\\u200fAmazing Food and Service \\u2013 Perfect for the Whole Family!\\n\\n\\u200fI recently had the pleasure of visiting OASIS!!  and I can\\u2019t say enough good things about this place! From the moment we walked in, the staff welcomed us with warm smiles and exceptional hospitality. The atmosphere was cozy and inviting, making it the perfect spot for a family meal.\\n\\n\\u200fNow, let\\u2019s talk about the food\\u2014absolutely phenomenal! The pasta dishes were cooked to perfection, with rich and flavorful sauces that clearly showcased the chef\\u2019s expertise and love for fresh, quality ingredients. The pastries were divine, with a buttery, flaky texture and just the right amount of sweetness. Every bite tasted homemade and full of heart!\\n\\n\\u200fWhat truly stood out was the attention to detail and the commitment to maintaining a high standard of kosher food. It\\u2019s not easy to find a place that balances authenticity and adherence to kosher guidelines so effortlessly. Everything was fresh, beautifully presented, and bursting with flavor.\\n\\n\\u200fThe service was equally impressive\\u2014fast, efficient, and always with a personal touch. They made us feel at home and went above and beyond to ensure we had a fantastic dining experience.\\n\\n\\u200fIf you\\u2019re looking for a place that offers incredible food, warm service, and an environment perfect for the whole family, look no further than  OASIS !!!\\n\\u200f I can\\u2019t wait to return and try even more from their amazing menu. Highly recommended!", "time": 1748195811, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Yael M", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109119853584570000839/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6kTCjG8rduOothegFy9xj4zmT6TtDvP7bWl146nE2Id7z2w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago", "text": "Ate here with the whole family and everyone enjoyed the food!!! Pizza was delicious thin yet