ir prices aren't.", "time": 1750260899, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Tziporah T", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105486272307837757705/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrMKivaHbrthjCZLrqFEt8_UnkyaYQQJEKiMhzreH_sczd9VE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "6 months ago", "text": "This place is absolutely gorgeous and has delicious food.I can't even count how many times I've been here with my family it's always amazing.I love the fish and chips,fried mushroom dumplings,crispy fried cheese, sandwiches,and mushrooms linguine.For dessert we always have the creme brulee which is an amazing way to finish an amazing meal. Highly recommend", "time": 1739073790, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "dylan murphy", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118415154142772691044/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhY10hbFFtX82HbsBMwDGE9FdZVGZe3rbE2YYAf_yfo4AGrkllfg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6", "rating": 4, "relative_time_description": "6 months ago", "text": "The food was well made. Never having Israeli food before we did not know what to expect and ordered items we didn't recognize to explore. The kiva was devine, very light and flaky with lovely tastes.\\n\\nService on the other hand was lacking. Our waitress only had 3 tables yet kept ignoring us and failing to checkin if we wanted or needed anything else. We had been eyeing a desert to try but after she walked by 3 times after bringing us the desert menu and not asking if we wanted to order we finally just asked for the check. The other wait staff seemed to be more attentive to their tables - wish we had been sat in their section!", "time": 1739284754, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Yossi Tabak", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111932642304689865481/r