9/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMPiRhiCZc6A2G4zbt5vp5LWqpRjHJZ87_DXXKRZI4c37ag5QP=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "a month ago", "text": "We have lived here 3+ years and somehow not known about this incredible place!\\n\\n10 stars for us !\\n\\nBest hummus and falafel and Jerusalem grill hummus. Hot fluffy pita bread. We took quite a bit home - ample portions. Fair prices\\n\\nWhile we waited I munched on the complimentary pickled carrots & slaw. Tangy. Delicious.\\n\\nWonderful customer service. Glad someone told us about this place!!", "time": 1751828578, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Chi Ngo", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112127771716792281185/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEeXl7ROJpCffFvOR7l2pNXw5AosdKPE7ZDdE31aXv7Sc9MrvZFg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 1, "relative_time_description": "in the last week", "text": "Closed when we showed up at 12:45pm on a Sunday, although their website and Google profile shows open on Sundays 11am\\u20139pm.\\n\\nEdit: Owner replied that they closed due to a religious holiday.  Understandable; however, the business should take a moment to proactively update its hours via its Google Business Profile (and website) so that potential customers are informed.", "time": 1754606334, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Max Mahairy", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114339651498564634974/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl7Q5WkRQkqye0qF6AfZpWFthH9nd6iKJcm6vxmMHLbqk_Uso=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "5 months ago", "text": "Top 3 middle eastern restaurants in all of Florida\\nBest food best service and best people\\nI\\u2019ll reco