is was nothing like the photos and other reviews. I was met with frustration as the woman said \\u201cwe close at 3pm\\u201d and it was only 2:40. Plenty of time for a quick to-go coffee. I ordered a coffee where they had added a $4.50 \\u201cmandatory\\u201d gratuity and stood there for over 15 minutes with only one other customer in the space waiting. The coffee was trash. Literally go anywhere else.", "time": 1752260967, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Isla Berger-Jara", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104459043912687473054/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3Gaf0140xjEu7FqshLv83oK3IZMT1nkGQyBARIB7SANvrM8kt=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "3 weeks ago", "text": "This place had no flaws, the service was literally amazing, instagram worthy pictures and the silverware and plates are to die for. Food was so good I wouldn\\u2019t change a thing I got the Pesto Greek Pizza and it easily ranked my first spot in my heart the lychee raspberry drink hit the spot as well I even had to ask for the recipe. Overall the meal, place, scenery and the warm cookie all topped it off to be the best place ever. An amazing find.", "time": 1752714636, "translated": false}, {"author_name": "Fernando Lopez", "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111802369745506489081/reviews", "language": "en", "original_language": "en", "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbELT3c1tD-pBkZWy36F_SiekZzgnEFi2cvS-FGapjYHvxsYXf=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 5, "relative_time_description": "7 months ago", "text": "We went on Christmas Day because we wanted some quick coffees and they were open and fast service. We got inside and didn't wait any longer than 10 minutes. The employees were all very nice and attentive to us and the coffees were amazing. Highly suggest this place for a different experience in the he