, \\u201csour cream\\u201d (vegan of course) and pico de gallo. I couldn\\u2019t stop eating it. Now lets talk about the Angus Beef Skewers. Wow! Soft flavorful meat on a skewer with some onions and peppers. The meat was so tender and juicy, I honestly could\\u2019ve ended the meal here. Naturally, I wanted to try just one entr\\u00e9e. I went with the Ribeye steak medium rare, which was grilled to perfection. It was soft and flavorful. The Ribeye also came with a side of fries. I also ordered one drink as I was on vacation, I ordered the Golden Margarita. It was the perfect way to end the night. Here is my summary. Great service, really good food, and VERY well priced. The whole meal with tax was just over $200. In the NY/NJ area, a meal like this would be at least double the price. We were also out within an hour and a half of just walking in. Highly recommend.", "time": 1724887112}]	Kosher Miami	\N	(305) 763-8601	Restaurant	Monday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM\nTuesday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM\nWednesday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM\nThursday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM\nFriday: Closed\nSaturday: 8:00 – 11:00 PM\nSunday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM	\N	{"periods": [{"open": {"day": 0, "time": "1730"}, "close": {"day": 0, "time": "2230"}}, {"open": {"day": 1, "time": "1730"}, "close": {"day": 1, "time": "2230"}}, {"open": {"day": 2, "time": "1730"}, "close": {"day": 2, "time": "2230"}}, {"open": {"day": 3, "time": "1730"}, "close": {"day": 3, "time": "2230"}}, {"open": {"day": 4, "time": "1730"}, "close": {"day": 4, "time": "2230"}}, {"open": {"day": 6, "time": "2000"}, "close": {"day": 6, "time": "2300"}}], "open_now": false, "weekday_text": ["Monday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM", "Tuesday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM", "Wednesday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM", "Thursday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM", "Friday: Closed", "Saturday: 8:00 – 11:00 PM", "Sunday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM"]}	\N	Meat	f	\N	\N	f	ChIJ6f150q-z2YgRclix0fuJufg	9477 Harding Ave, Surfside, FL 33154, USA	2025-08-12 05:33:28.147231	restaurant	[{"author": "Moshe Moeller", "rating": 5, "text": "We had an outstan